  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Medicines and medical products: continuity of supply update
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    A letter to suppliers giving an update on ensuring a continued supply of medicines and medical products if the UK leaves the EU with no deal.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

